(1,	'2017-11-23 06:38:27',	'2017-11-23 06:38:27',	'What is a Ondemandservicemarketplace.com?',	'A Ondemandservicemarketplace.com is a dog sitter - they love dogs, caring for them in their own home as if they were part of their own family. Each of our reliable assistants has been vetted by us and reviewed by other assistant.'),
(2,	'2017-11-23 06:38:27',	'2017-11-23 06:38:27',	'How does it work?',	'We provide an easy way to find and book a reliable and caring dog sitter in your local area, in a few simple steps online. For added peace of mind all bookings are covered by vet and public liability insurance as well as 24/7 emergency veterinary support.'),
(3,	'2017-11-23 06:38:27',	'2017-11-23 06:38:27',	'What services are available?',	'You can choose from \'Dog Boarding\' (24 hours - day and night - in the assistant\'s home), \'Dog Day Care\' (during the day only), and \'Dog Walking\'. Our dog sitters may offer all, or some of these services, as displayed on their listing.'),
(4,	'2017-11-23 06:38:27',	'2017-11-23 06:38:27',	'How do I book?',	'After you send a reservation request your assistant will have 24 hours to confirm or decline. You will only be charged when your booking is confirmed.'),
(5,	'2017-11-23 06:38:27',	'2017-11-23 06:38:27',	'Can I meet the assistant before the booking starts?',	'Of course! After your booking is confirmed, you can arrange a \'meet & greet\' - a chance for your dog and their new assistant to get to know each other before the booking begins.'),
